{
  "video_id": "zwpiI18TBdE",
  "title": "Inside the mind of a former radical jihadist | Manwar Ali",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12760.0,
      "end_time": 16776.0,
      "text": "Today I stand before you as a man who lives life to the full"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16800.0,
      "end_time": 18400.0,
      "text": "in the here and now."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19280.0,
      "end_time": 20936.0,
      "text": "But for a long time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20960.0,
      "end_time": 22160.0,
      "text": "I lived for death."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23920.0,
      "end_time": 25536.0,
      "text": "I was a young man who believed"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25560.0,
      "end_time": 30119.0,
      "text": "that jihad is to be understood in the language of force and violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32759.0,
      "end_time": 36000.0,
      "text": "I tried to right wrongs through power and aggression."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 37440.0,
      "end_time": 41879.0,
      "text": "I had deep concerns for the suffering of others"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 42760.0,
      "end_time": 46000.0,
      "text": "and a strong desire to help and bring relief to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 49120.0,
      "end_time": 52455.0,
      "text": "I thought violent jihad was noble,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 52480.0,
      "end_time": 53815.0,
      "text": "chivalrous"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 53840.0,
      "end_time": 55160.0,
      "text": "and the best way to help."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 57640.0,
      "end_time": 59536.0,
      "text": "At a time when so many of our people --"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 59560.0,
      "end_time": 60816.0,
      "text": "young people especially --"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 60840.0,
      "end_time": 62400.0,
      "text": "are at risk of radicalization"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 63400.0,
      "end_time": 65960.0,
      "text": "through groups like al-Qaeda,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 65120.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66960.0,
      "text": "Islamic State and others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 67880.0,
      "end_time": 69336.0,
      "text": "when these groups are claiming"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 69360.0,
      "end_time": 74416.0,
      "text": "that their horrific brutality and violence are true jihad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 74440.0,
      "end_time": 78616.0,
      "text": "I want to say that their idea of jihad is wrong --"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 78640.0,
      "end_time": 79976.0,
      "text": "completely wrong --"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 80000.0,
      "end_time": 81200.0,
      "text": "as was mine, then."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 83200.0,
      "end_time": 85560.0,
      "text": "Jihad means to strive to one&#39;s utmost."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 86440.0,
      "end_time": 89456.0,
      "text": "It includes exertion and spirituality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 89480.0,
      "end_time": 90976.0,
      "text": "self-purification"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 91000.0,
      "end_time": 92200.0,
      "text": "and devotion."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 94480.0,
      "end_time": 97256.0,
      "text": "It refers to positive transformation"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 97280.0,
      "end_time": 101376.0,
      "text": "through learning, wisdom and remembrance of God."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 101400.0,
      "end_time": 104640.0,
      "text": "The word jihad stands for all those meanings as a whole."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 106920.0,
      "end_time": 111336.0,
      "text": "Jihad may at times take the form of fighting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 111360.0,
      "end_time": 112560.0,
      "text": "but only sometimes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 113200.0,
      "end_time": 114920.0,
      "text": "under strict conditions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 116200.0,
      "end_time": 118160.0,
      "text": "within rules and limits."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 119840.0,
      "end_time": 121560.0,
      "text": "In Islam,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 121800.0,
      "end_time": 126800.0,
      "text": "the benefit of an act must outweigh the harm or hardship it entails."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 127240.0,
      "end_time": 128976.0,
      "text": "More importantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 129000.0,
      "end_time": 133736.0,
      "text": "the verses in the Koran that are connected to jihad or fighting"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 133760.0,
      "end_time": 139335.0,
      "text": "do not cancel out the verses that talk about forgiveness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 139360.0,
      "end_time": 140656.0,
      "text": "benevolence"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 140680.0,
      "end_time": 141880.0,
      "text": "or patience."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 145320.0,
      "end_time": 149896.0,
      "text": "But now I believe that there are no circumstances on earth"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 149920.0,
      "end_time": 152495.0,
      "text": "where violent jihad is permissible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 152520.0,
      "end_time": 155200.0,
      "text": "because it will lead to greater harm."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 157800.0,
      "end_time": 160296.0,
      "text": "But now the idea of jihad has been hijacked."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 160320.0,
      "end_time": 163656.0,
      "text": "It has been perverted to mean violent struggle"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 163680.0,
      "end_time": 166656.0,
      "text": "wherever Muslims are undergoing difficulties,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 166680.0,
      "end_time": 168576.0,
      "text": "and turned into terrorism"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 168600.0,
      "end_time": 171656.0,
      "text": "by fascistic Islamists like al-Qaeda,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 171680.0,
      "end_time": 173240.0,
      "text": "Islamic State and others."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 174280.0,
      "end_time": 176256.0,
      "text": "But I have come to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 176280.0,
      "end_time": 180216.0,
      "text": "that true jihad means striving to the utmost"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 180240.0,
      "end_time": 183600.0,
      "text": "to strengthen and live those qualities which God loves:"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 184440.0,
      "end_time": 186776.0,
      "text": "honesty, trustworthiness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 186800.0,
      "end_time": 188896.0,
      "text": "compassion, benevolence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 188920.0,
      "end_time": 190815.0,
      "text": "reliability, respect,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 190840.0,
      "end_time": 192216.0,
      "text": "truthfulness --"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 192240.0,
      "end_time": 195360.0,
      "text": "human values that so many of us share."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 198360.0,
      "end_time": 200216.0,
      "text": "I was born in Bangladesh,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 200240.0,
      "end_time": 201669.0,
      "text": "but grew up mostly in England."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 202480.0,
      "end_time": 203719.0,
      "text": "And I went to school here."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 204480.0,
      "end_time": 206775.0,
      "text": "My father was an academic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 206800.0,
      "end_time": 208880.0,
      "text": "and we were in the UK through his work."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 210360.0,
      "end_time": 214840.0,
      "text": "In 1971 we were in Bangladesh when everything changed."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 216240.0,
      "end_time": 219776.0,
      "text": "The War of Independence impacted upon us terribly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 219800.0,
      "end_time": 221656.0,
      "text": "pitting family against family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 221680.0,
      "end_time": 223376.0,
      "text": "neighbor against neighbor."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 223400.0,
      "end_time": 226256.0,
      "text": "And at the age of 12 I experienced war,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 226280.0,
      "end_time": 227880.0,
      "text": "destitution in my family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 228720.0,
      "end_time": 231960.0,
      "text": "the deaths of 22 of my relatives in horrible ways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 232960.0,
      "end_time": 235760.0,
      "text": "as well as the murder of my elder brother."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 239400.0,
      "end_time": 240799.0,
      "text": "I witnessed killing ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 243000.0,
      "end_time": 245816.0,
      "text": "animals feeding on corpses in the streets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 245840.0,
      "end_time": 247576.0,
      "text": "starvation all around me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 247600.0,
      "end_time": 249736.0,
      "text": "wanton, horrific violence --"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 249760.0,
      "end_time": 250959.0,
      "text": "senseless violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 254280.0,
      "end_time": 256160.0,
      "text": "I was a young man,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 256399.99999999997,
      "end_time": 258975.99999999997,
      "text": "teenager, fascinated by ideas."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 259000.0,
      "end_time": 260815.0,
      "text": "I wanted to learn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 260839.0,
      "end_time": 262888.0,
      "text": "but I could not go to school for four years."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 264760.0,
      "end_time": 266216.0,
      "text": "After the War of Independence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 266240.0,
      "end_time": 268720.0,
      "text": "my father was put in prison for two and a half years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 269839.0,
      "end_time": 272360.0,
      "text": "and I used to visit him every week in prison,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 273120.0,
      "end_time": 274600.0,
      "text": "and homeschooled myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 276800.0,
      "end_time": 278640.0,
      "text": "My father was released in 1973"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 279520.0,
      "end_time": 282960.0,
      "text": "and he fled to England as a refugee,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 282120.0,
      "end_time": 283360.0,
      "text": "and we soon followed him."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 284720.0,
      "end_time": 286376.0,
      "text": "I was 17."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 286400.0,
      "end_time": 288856.0,
      "text": "So these experiences gave me"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 288880.0,
      "end_time": 292680.0,
      "text": "a sharp awareness of the atrocities and injustices in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 294320.0,
      "end_time": 296135.0,
      "text": "And I had a strong desire --"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 296160.0,
      "end_time": 298176.0,
      "text": "a very keen, deep desire --"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 298200.0,
      "end_time": 299416.0,
      "text": "to right wrongs"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 299440.0,
      "end_time": 301107.0,
      "text": "and help the victims of oppression."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 302600.0,
      "end_time": 304536.0,
      "text": "While studying at college in the UK,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 304560.0,
      "end_time": 310400.0,
      "text": "I met others who showed me how I could channel that desire"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 310720.0,
      "end_time": 312440.0,
      "text": "and help through my religion."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 313720.0,
      "end_time": 315160.0,
      "text": "And I was radicalized --"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 315400.0,
      "end_time": 318480.0,
      "text": "enough to consider violence correct,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 319640.0,
      "end_time": 322000.0,
      "text": "even a virtue under certain circumstances."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 324320.0,
      "end_time": 327536.0,
      "text": "So I became involved in the jihad in Afghanistan."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 327560.0,
      "end_time": 332120.0,
      "text": "I wanted to protect the Muslim Afghan population against the Soviet army."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 332960.0,
      "end_time": 335335.0,
      "text": "And I thought that was jihad:"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 335360.0,
      "end_time": 336856.0,
      "text": "my sacred duty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 336880.0,
      "end_time": 338600.0,
      "text": "which would be rewarded by God."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 343880.0,
      "end_time": 345880.0,
      "text": "I became a preacher."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 347960.0,
      "end_time": 353560.0,
      "text": "I was one of the pioneers of violent jihad in the UK."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 353800.0,
      "end_time": 354575.0,
      "text": "I recruited,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 354600.0,
      "end_time": 356280.0,
      "text": "I raised funds, I trained."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 357360.0,
      "end_time": 359896.0,
      "text": "I confused true jihad"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 359920.0,
      "end_time": 363920.0,
      "text": "with this perversion as presented by the fascist Islamists --"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 365680.0,
      "end_time": 368736.0,
      "text": "these people who use the idea of jihad"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 368760.0,
      "end_time": 372640.0,
      "text": "to justify their lust for power, authority and control on earth:"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 373745.0,
      "end_time": 378560.0,
      "text": "a perversion perpetuated today by fascist Islamist groups"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 378800.0,
      "end_time": 380960.0,
      "text": "like al-Qaeda, Islamic State and others."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 382440.0,
      "end_time": 384280.0,
      "text": "For a period of around 15 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 385480.0,
      "end_time": 389280.0,
      "text": "I fought for short periods of time"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 390240.0,
      "end_time": 391976.0,
      "text": "in Kashmir and Burma,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 392000.0,
      "end_time": 393320.0,
      "text": "besides Afghanistan."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 397000.0,
      "end_time": 399720.0,
      "text": "Our aim was to remove the invaders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 400760.0,
      "end_time": 403840.0,
      "text": "to bring relief to the oppressed victims"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 404880.0,
      "end_time": 408160.0,
      "text": "and of course to establish an Islamic state,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 408400.0,
      "end_time": 409760.0,
      "text": "a caliphate for God&#39;s rule."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 410720.0,
      "end_time": 411920.0,
      "text": "And I did this openly."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 413480.0,
      "end_time": 415760.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t break any laws."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 416440.0,
      "end_time": 419536.0,
      "text": "I was proud and grateful to be British --"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 419560.0,
      "end_time": 421136.0,
      "text": "I still am."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 421160.0,
      "end_time": 424800.0,
      "text": "And I bore no hostility against this, my country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 425960.0,
      "end_time": 429496.0,
      "text": "nor enmity towards the non-Muslim citizens,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 429520.0,
      "end_time": 430919.0,
      "text": "and I still don&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 433840.0,
      "end_time": 436215.0,
      "text": "During one battle in Afghanistan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 436240.0,
      "end_time": 439120.0,
      "text": "some British men and I formed a special bond"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 439960.0,
      "end_time": 442695.0,
      "text": "with a 15-year-old Afghani boy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 442720.0,
      "end_time": 443920.0,
      "text": "Abdullah,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 444840.0,
      "end_time": 447176.0,
      "text": "an innocent, loving and lovable kid"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 447200.0,
      "end_time": 449240.0,
      "text": "who was always eager to please."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 450960.0,
      "end_time": 452159.0,
      "text": "He was poor."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 452760.0,
      "end_time": 455480.0,
      "text": "And boys like him did menial tasks in the camp."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 456480.0,
      "end_time": 457766.0,
      "text": "And he seemed happy enough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 458480.0,
      "end_time": 459896.0,
      "text": "but I couldn&#39;t help wonder --"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 459920.0,
      "end_time": 461825.0,
      "text": "his parents must have missed him dearly."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 463560.0,
      "end_time": 467120.0,
      "text": "And they must have dreamt about a better future for him."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 469560.0,
      "end_time": 472376.0,
      "text": "A victim of circumstance caught up in a war,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 472400.0,
      "end_time": 473679.0,
      "text": "cruelly thrust upon him"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 474720.0,
      "end_time": 476960.0,
      "text": "by the cruel circumstances of the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 480680.0,
      "end_time": 485400.0,
      "text": "One day I picked up this unexploded mortar shell in a trench,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 486320.0,
      "end_time": 490120.0,
      "text": "and I had it deposited in a makeshift mud hut lab."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 491280.0,
      "end_time": 494215.0,
      "text": "And I went out on a short, pointless skirmish --"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 494240.0,
      "end_time": 495440.0,
      "text": "always pointless,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 496440.0,
      "end_time": 499880.0,
      "text": "And I came back a few hours later to discover he was dead."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 501160.0,
      "end_time": 503936.0,
      "text": "He had tried to recover explosives from that shell."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 503960.0,
      "end_time": 506560.0,
      "text": "It exploded, and he died a violent death,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 507440.0,
      "end_time": 511719.0,
      "text": "blown to bits by the very same device that had proved harmless to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 513799.99999999994,
      "end_time": 514599.99999999994,
      "text": "So I started to question."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 516600.0,
      "end_time": 520320.0,
      "text": "How did his death serve any purpose?"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 522280.0,
      "end_time": 524280.0,
      "text": "Why did he die and I lived?"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 525559.0,
      "end_time": 527550.0,
      "text": "I carried on."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 527800.0,
      "end_time": 528696.0,
      "text": "I fought in Kashmir."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 528720.0,
      "end_time": 531416.0,
      "text": "I also recruited for the Philippines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 531440.0,
      "end_time": 533240.0,
      "text": "Bosnia and Chechnya."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 534559.0,
      "end_time": 535839.0,
      "text": "And the questions grew."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 537880.0,
      "end_time": 539776.0,
      "text": "Later in Burma,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 539800.0,
      "end_time": 542136.0,
      "text": "I came across Rohingya fighters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 542160.0,
      "end_time": 544415.0,
      "text": "who were barely teenagers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 544440.0,
      "end_time": 546960.0,
      "text": "born and brought up in the jungle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 546120.0,
      "end_time": 548180.0,
      "text": "carrying machine guns and grenade launchers."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 552000.0,
      "end_time": 557200.0,
      "text": "I met two 13-year-olds with soft manners and gentle voices."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 558920.0,
      "end_time": 560136.0,
      "text": "Looking at me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 560160.0,
      "end_time": 562240.0,
      "text": "they begged me to take them away to England."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 568720.0,
      "end_time": 570600.0,
      "text": "They simply wanted to go to school --"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 571680.0,
      "end_time": 573000.0,
      "text": "that was their dream."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 576360.0,
      "end_time": 577576.0,
      "text": "My family --"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 577600.0,
      "end_time": 579560.0,
      "text": "my children of the same age --"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 579800.0,
      "end_time": 581400.0,
      "text": "were living at home in the UK,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 582400.0,
      "end_time": 583336.0,
      "text": "going to school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 583360.0,
      "end_time": 584560.0,
      "text": "living a safe life."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 585880.0,
      "end_time": 587136.0,
      "text": "And I couldn&#39;t help wonder"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 587160.0,
      "end_time": 590616.0,
      "text": "how much these young boys must have spoken to one another"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 590640.0,
      "end_time": 592840.0,
      "text": "about their dreams for such a life."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 594920.0,
      "end_time": 596839.0,
      "text": "Victims of circumstances:"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 598360.0,
      "end_time": 599640.0,
      "text": "these two young boys,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 600320.0,
      "end_time": 603376.0,
      "text": "sleeping rough on the ground, looking up at the stars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 603400.0,
      "end_time": 605896.0,
      "text": "cynically exploited by their leaders"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 605920.0,
      "end_time": 608400.0,
      "text": "for their personal lust for glory and power."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 609920.0,
      "end_time": 613136.0,
      "text": "I soon witnessed boys like them killing one another"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 613160.0,
      "end_time": 615400.0,
      "text": "in conflicts between rival groups."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 617400.0,
      "end_time": 619760.0,
      "text": "And it was the same everywhere ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 621280.0,
      "end_time": 623776.0,
      "text": "Afghanistan, Kashmir, Burma,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 623800.0,
      "end_time": 625280.0,
      "text": "Philippines, Chechnya;"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 626240.0,
      "end_time": 630856.0,
      "text": "petty warlords got the young and vulnerable to kill one another"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 630880.0,
      "end_time": 632200.0,
      "text": "in the name of jihad."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 634240.0,
      "end_time": 636800.0,
      "text": "Muslims against Muslims."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 637640.0,
      "end_time": 642160.0,
      "text": "Not protecting anyone against invaders or occupiers;"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 642400.0,
      "end_time": 644400.0,
      "text": "not bringing relief to the oppressed."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 646240.0,
      "end_time": 647616.0,
      "text": "Children being used,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 647640.0,
      "end_time": 649256.0,
      "text": "cynically exploited;"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 649280.0,
      "end_time": 651216.0,
      "text": "people dying in conflicts"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 651240.0,
      "end_time": 654280.0,
      "text": "which I was supporting in the name of jihad."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 656920.0,
      "end_time": 658560.0,
      "text": "And it still carries on today."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 663800.0,
      "end_time": 667415.0,
      "text": "Realizing that the violent jihad"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 667440.0,
      "end_time": 671640.0,
      "text": "I had engaged in abroad"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 673440.0,
      "end_time": 675480.0,
      "text": "was so different --"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 677280.0,
      "end_time": 682160.0,
      "text": "such a chasm between what I had experienced"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 682400.0,
      "end_time": 683839.0,
      "text": "and what I thought was sacred duty --"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 684640.0,
      "end_time": 687600.0,
      "text": "I had to reflect on my activities here in the UK."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 690240.0,
      "end_time": 692296.0,
      "text": "I had to consider my preaching,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 692320.0,
      "end_time": 693856.0,
      "text": "recruiting, fund-raising,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 693880.0,
      "end_time": 695456.0,
      "text": "training,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 695480.0,
      "end_time": 697600.0,
      "text": "but most importantly, radicalizing --"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 698640.0,
      "end_time": 700856.0,
      "text": "sending young people to fight and die"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 700880.0,
      "end_time": 702960.0,
      "text": "as I was doing --"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 702120.0,
      "end_time": 703880.0,
      "text": "all totally wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 707680.0,
      "end_time": 710880.0,
      "text": "So I got involved in violent jihad in the mid &#39;80s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 711960.0,
      "end_time": 713440.0,
      "text": "starting with Afghanistan."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 714600.0,
      "end_time": 717880.0,
      "text": "And by the time I finished it was in the year 2000."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 719400.0,
      "end_time": 720616.0,
      "text": "I was completely immersed in it."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 720640.0,
      "end_time": 722576.0,
      "text": "All around me people supported,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 722600.0,
      "end_time": 723816.0,
      "text": "applauded,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 723840.0,
      "end_time": 726240.0,
      "text": "even celebrated what we were doing in their name."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 728160.0,
      "end_time": 729976.0,
      "text": "But by the time I learned to get out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 730000.0,
      "end_time": 732616.0,
      "text": "completely disillusioned in the year 2000,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 732640.0,
      "end_time": 734319.0,
      "text": "15 years had passed."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 737200.0,
      "end_time": 738440.0,
      "text": "So what goes wrong?"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 740720.0,
      "end_time": 743560.0,
      "text": "We were so busy talking about virtue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 745160.0,
      "end_time": 748319.0,
      "text": "and we were blinded by a cause."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 752240.0,
      "end_time": 756520.0,
      "text": "And we did not give ourselves a chance to develop a virtuous character."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 757680.0,
      "end_time": 761815.0,
      "text": "We told ourselves we were fighting for the oppressed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 761840.0,
      "end_time": 764400.0,
      "text": "but these were unwinnable wars."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 765720.0,
      "end_time": 769336.0,
      "text": "We became the very instrument through which more deaths occurred,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 769360.0,
      "end_time": 773960.0,
      "text": "complicit in causing further misery"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 773120.0,
      "end_time": 775720.0,
      "text": "for the selfish benefit of the cruel few."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 784280.0,
      "end_time": 785496.0,
      "text": "So over time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 785520.0,
      "end_time": 786720.0,
      "text": "a very long time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 788600.0,
      "end_time": 789800.0,
      "text": "I opened my eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 791960.0,
      "end_time": 793440.0,
      "text": "I began to dare"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 795400.0,
      "end_time": 796695.0,
      "text": "to face the truth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 796720.0,
      "end_time": 797920.0,
      "text": "to think,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 799360.0,
      "end_time": 801496.0,
      "text": "to face the hard questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 801520.0,
      "end_time": 803720.0,
      "text": "I got in touch with my soul."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 814800.0,
      "end_time": 815400.0,
      "text": "What have I learned?"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 816640.0,
      "end_time": 821199.0,
      "text": "That people who engage in violent jihadism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 822960.0,
      "end_time": 825560.0,
      "text": "that people who are drawn to these types of extremisms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 826600.0,
      "end_time": 828800.0,
      "text": "are not that different to everyone else."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 829880.0,
      "end_time": 832680.0,
      "text": "But I believe such people can change."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 834120.0,
      "end_time": 836976.0,
      "text": "They can regain their hearts and restore them"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 837000.0,
      "end_time": 840600.0,
      "text": "by filling them with human values that heal."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 847000.0,
      "end_time": 849216.0,
      "text": "When we ignore the realities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 849240.0,
      "end_time": 855000.0,
      "text": "we discover that we accept what we are told without critical reflection."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 857640.0,
      "end_time": 861415.0,
      "text": "And we ignore the gifts and advantages that many of us would cherish"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 861440.0,
      "end_time": 863720.0,
      "text": "even for a single moment in their lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 868400.0,
      "end_time": 870760.0,
      "text": "I engaged in actions I thought were correct."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 873760.0,
      "end_time": 877760.0,
      "text": "But now I began to question how I knew what I knew."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 879840.0,
      "end_time": 883536.0,
      "text": "I endlessly told others to accept the truth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 883560.0,
      "end_time": 887280.0,
      "text": "but I failed to give doubt its rightful place."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 892920.0,
      "end_time": 897776.0,
      "text": "This conviction that people can change is rooted in my experience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 897800.0,
      "end_time": 899000.0,
      "text": "my own journey."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 900520.0,
      "end_time": 902415.0,
      "text": "Through wide reading,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 902440.0,
      "end_time": 903640.0,
      "text": "reflecting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 904160.0,
      "end_time": 906550.0,
      "text": "contemplation, self-knowledge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 906800.0,
      "end_time": 907296.0,
      "text": "I discovered,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 907320.0,
      "end_time": 912960.0,
      "text": "I realized that Islamists&#39; world of us and them is false and unjust."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 916800.0,
      "end_time": 920479.0,
      "text": "Through considering the uncertainties in all that we had asserted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 921400.0,
      "end_time": 923160.0,
      "text": "to the inviolable truths,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 923400.0,
      "end_time": 924439.0,
      "text": "incontestable truths,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 926960.0,
      "end_time": 929840.0,
      "text": "I developed a more nuanced understanding."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 936480.0,
      "end_time": 940960.0,
      "text": "I realized that in a world crowded with variation and contradiction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 941920.0,
      "end_time": 943136.0,
      "text": "foolish preachers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 943160.0,
      "end_time": 946175.0,
      "text": "only foolish preachers like I used to be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 946200.0,
      "end_time": 951560.0,
      "text": "see no paradox in the myths and fictions they use to assert authenticity."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 953120.0,
      "end_time": 957656.0,
      "text": "So I understood the vital importance of self-knowledge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 957680.0,
      "end_time": 958880.0,
      "text": "political awareness"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 960000.0,
      "end_time": 964656.0,
      "text": "and the necessity for a deep and wide understanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 964680.0,
      "end_time": 967136.0,
      "text": "of our commitments and our actions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 967160.0,
      "end_time": 968480.0,
      "text": "how they affect others."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 970520.0,
      "end_time": 971976.0,
      "text": "So my plea today to everyone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 972000.0,
      "end_time": 976480.0,
      "text": "especially those who sincerely believe in Islamist jihadism ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 978480.0,
      "end_time": 980880.0,
      "text": "refuse dogmatic authority;"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 982360.0,
      "end_time": 986400.0,
      "text": "let go of anger, hatred and violence;"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 987120.0,
      "end_time": 988776.0,
      "text": "learn to right wrongs"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 988800.0,
      "end_time": 993870.0,
      "text": "without even attempting to justify cruel, unjust and futile behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
